    "Mac never drains motor; dispatch upgrades blocked paths to CF tick.",
    "Self-improvement items enter Kaizen backlog with value_class; >30% none spend → THROTTLED_ROI.",
    "Public Brain answers cite brain_registry assets — signal-factory, controlled-autorun, locked-definitions."
